&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/wiapost/5255-What-is-Sin.jpg" alt="What-is-Sin" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">What Is Sin?
&lt;div id="what-is-sin" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#what-is-sin" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>You lose a loved one, a bond, or your health,&lt;br>
Blame it on God, Fate, or Karma’s stealth.&lt;br>
You feel consoled, the burden shared,&lt;br>
But deep within, you&amp;rsquo;re still ensnared.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>You blame the system, the people, the ways,&lt;br>
And disgust fills the remaining days.&lt;br>
But no matter where the blame is cast,&lt;br>
The suffering lingers, it seems to last.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Cause Of Pain And Suffering</title><link>https://dasarpai.github.io/wiaposts/cause-of-pain-and-suffering/</link><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author><guid>https://dasarpai.github.io/wiaposts/cause-of-pain-and-suffering/</guid><description>&lt;p>
&lt;figure>
&lt;img class="my-0 rounded-md" loading="lazy" src="https://dasarpai.github.io/assets/images/wiapost/5124-Cause-Of-Pain-And-Suffering.jpg" alt="Cause Of Pain And Suffering" />
&lt;/figure>
&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 class="relative group">Cause Of Pain And Suffering
&lt;div id="cause-of-pain-and-suffering" class="anchor">&lt;/div>
&lt;span
class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100">
&lt;a class="group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700"
style="text-decoration-line: none !important;" href="#cause-of-pain-and-suffering" aria-label="Anchor">#&lt;/a>
&lt;/span>
&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>I am a body. &lt;br>
Therefore I must have pain and comfort. &lt;br>
And I can cause pain and comfort for others.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>I am a mind. &lt;br>
Therefore I feel love and hate for others. &lt;br>
Hence I feel enjoyment and suffering. &lt;br>
And as a mind, I can cause enjoyment and suffering for others.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>